    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Revenue Manager with drive and ambition, Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions in Varanasi is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions:\nAnanda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions!",
